---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Next LX: A Flight Simulator for Office Work"
  description="Next LX was an experimental employment agency that represented high potential workers who have been skilled to spec in an AI-powered workplace simulator."
  url="https://sociotechnica.org/next-lx"
  image="https://sociotechnica.org/sociotechnica-social.png"
>
  <h1 class="text-4xl mb-5 font-serif">Next LX</h1>
  <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-1">July-December 2024</p>

  <article class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
    <p class="mb-5">
      Next LX was an experimental employment agency that represented high potential workers who have
      been skilled to spec in an AI-powered workplace simulator.
    </p>
    <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-2xl">Project Updates</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-10">
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/10fGzcgXkPtau3RtUCHwpsOfTWf89YGyxFX9b02FcJs8/edit?tab=t.0"
          >Update #3: 10/23/24 - 12/20/24 (Final Update)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1r00gehxK9PVlbr2_YRidAHOkGdtoVTSIhZWkAF6fjV4/edit?tab=t.0"
          >Update #2: 9/15/24 - 10/23/24</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/18yqbsj2d3wTAr2T_16KJu-L-UlvMOGAl5AN6rgkkPQw/edit?tab=t.0"
          >Update #1: 7/1/24 - 9/15/24</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3 font-serif text-2xl">Product Demo Videos</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-10">
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://youtu.be/yb3gqac7hL4?si=GwarJIugMIUowduG">Week 12: September 26, 2024</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://youtu.be/TkC0VPSihiM?si=lvQL6drAOA2MuZyd">Week 7: August 21, 2024</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://youtu.be/owcaPCaBQFU?si=yisiSkIzVeRn9IWS"
          >Week 5: August 8, 2024: South Park Commons Demo Night</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://youtu.be/ktlhWdZbwO0?si=VEwsmngM_L3cQluF">Week 2: July 19, 2024</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-1">
        <a
          class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
          href="https://youtu.be/W2EE-V4Y5a4?si=rHnMsTxuHUG-pM78">Week 1: July 12, 2024</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-5 mb-5">
      Related: <a
        class="border-b-2 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-yellow-700 hover:text-yellow-700"
        href="/simulation">The Power of Simulation-Based Training for Office Work</a
      >
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>